BEGIN_TEXT

Find the linear approximation of \( f(x)=\ln x \) at \( x=1 \) and use it to estimate \( \ln $a \). 
$BR
\(L(x)=\) \{ans_rule(10)\}
$BR
\(\ln $a \approx\) \{ans_rule(10)\}

END_TEXT

